code: @Override public DataSet<Edge<K, Tuple3<EV, Degrees, Degrees>>> runInternal(Graph<K, VV, EV> input) throws Exception {     // s, t, d(s)     DataSet<Edge<K, Tuple2<EV, Degrees>>> edgeSourceDegrees = input.run(new EdgeSourceDegrees<K, VV, EV>().setParallelism(parallelism)).     // t, d(t)     DataSet<Vertex<K, Degrees>> vertexDegrees = input.run(new VertexDegrees<K, VV, EV>().setParallelism(parallelism)).     // s, t, (d(s), d(t))     return edgeSourceDegrees.join(vertexDegrees, JoinHint.REPARTITION_HASH_SECOND).where(1).equalTo(0).with(new JoinEdgeDegreeWithVertexDegree<>()).setParallelism(parallelism).name("Edge target degree"). }
